Subject: [PATCH] Build Roslyn as net6.0 in source-build

Set compilers package targetframework to net6.0.
Update _RoslynTargetDirectoryName for net6.0

Fixups for new types and changes introduced with net5.0:

* Disable some warnings to let code continue to compile.

* Remove S.Runtime.InteropServices.WindowsRuntime using. Doesn't exist
  and doesn't seem necessary in net6.0.
